snippet.title: Gate 88 - Me Against The Universe - (Free Games) Gameplay No Commentary/Oldschool Arcade Games (Pc)
snippet.description:
Don't forget to like and subscribe to become a true Gemini here: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkUCodEd3HiLt9Iniy3nznQ

Here we have another free game for you guy's to try out, Gate 88 is an oldschool arcade type space shooter game it's cool, unfortanatly you're on you're own against hundread's of enemy's and enemy bases yes sound's impossible right well it pretty much is, it was an onling game back in the late 90s or early 2000s I forget which but without online you're by yourself you can build turret's to protect you're main base and other structure's you build but even at that it's hard, you have to protect you're main base from being destroyed but you also have to take out there bases numorous bases so the task of protecting you're own and destroying there's at the same time make's this game damn near impossible...so enjoy and until next time stay cool.

Go check out these channel's below:

Gemini beats 4life: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCXbomDZemdnokidmXF7Au-w

Gemini Queen: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCVt6W8tC38-pZNXQ5wyUrnQ

Gemini King - Topic: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkUCodEd3HiLt9Iniy3nznQ

Gemini King: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCxI2gYx5lr8eTWI2FxB9luQ

The Official YDB:  https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9q-vgHA27RQTkGpl-GVH-w

Purdy Gaming: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8PoC2hAspkKIx1_pqoq04A

XenWeezSan: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtk-DbBu0Ce0S4998UiI5UQ

Created by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King)

Edited by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King)

Gameplay done by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King)

Any lyrics done and performed by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King) And Jake John Tottenham (The Official YDB)

Music created by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King) And Jake John Tottenham (The Official YDB)

Outro created by: Ryan William Tottenham (Gemini King)

This gameplay took me more than a few hours to record edit and render...it seems lately I've had trouble's rendering these no commentary gameplays but we did it.

me against the entire universe this shit is intense... ;)
